- "Demographic details" include age group, gender, ethnicity, and turnout percentage;
- The query focuses on the districts where the winning candidates were elected.

sql:
SELECT candidate_id
FROM candidate_finance
WHERE donations > 500000;

SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM candidate_finance
WHERE CAST(donations AS REAL) > 500000 AND CAST(cash_on_hand AS REAL) > 100000;

